cast.overview: After nearly two decades of legendary criminal feats, making him France's most notorious criminal while simultaneously feeding his desire for media attention and public adoration, Mesrine becomes increasingly paranoid and isolated, leading to a dramatic confrontation with the law that ultimately seals his fate as the nation's most infamous public enemy.
cast.title: Mesrine: Public Enemy #1

details.biography:
Fanny Sidney, whose real name is Fanny Mauferon, is a French actress and director born April 5, 1987 in Paris.

Fanny Sidney attended classes at the Hector-Berlioz conservatory (2005-2006) then took part in the free class of Cours Florent"(2006-2009) before joining the "Direction" section of La Fémis (2011-2015). She is particularly known for her role of Camille Valentini in the series "Call my agent!". In 2019, she announced that she was pregnant with her first child.
